<html>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #000; padding: 20px">
    <p>Dear <strong><%= fullName %></strong>,</p>

    <p>
      We’re sorry to inform you that your order could not be processed at this
      time.
    </p>

    <p>
      <strong>Order ID:</strong> <%= orderId %><br />
      <strong>Order Date:</strong> <%= orderDate %><br />
      <strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %>
    </p>

    <p style="margin-top: 20px">
      <a
        href="https://v-s-store.onrender.com/orders"
        style="
          background-color: #4caf50;
          color: #fff;
          padding: 10px 20px;
          text-decoration: none;
          border-radius: 5px;
        "
      >
        Check Order Status
      </a>
    </p>

    <p>
      We apologize for the inconvenience. Please contact our support team if you
      need assistance or wish to place a new order.
    </p>

    <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>

    <p>— V&S Team</p>
  </body>
</html>
